      "survey_number": 4,
      "title": {
        "ko": "휴머노이드 로보틱스의 10년: ZMP에서 VLA까지",
        "en": "A Decade of Humanoid Robotics: From ZMP to VLA"
      },
      "description": {
        "ko": "2015–2026년 휴머노이드 대격변을 16개 챕터로 정리한 서베이. 정통파 LIPM/ZMP/MPC 스택의 한계, 네 기폭제(QDD·GPU 시뮬·teacher-student RL·sim-to-real), System 0/1/2 아키텍처와 VLA 통합, BD·Figure·Agility·Unitree·AgiBot 선두 기업 분석, 한국 제조피지컬AI 관점의 미래 확산 시나리오까지.",
        "en": "A 16-chapter survey of the humanoid robotics transformation from 2015 to 2026. Covers the limits of the orthodox LIPM/ZMP/MPC stack, the four catalysts (QDD actuators, GPU-parallel simulation, teacher-student RL, sim-to-real), the System 0/1/2 architecture with VLA integration, frontier-company analyses (Boston Dynamics, Figure, Agility, Unitree, AgiBot), and future diffusion scenarios through the lens of Korea's Manufacturing Physical AI."
